data.description: Welcome to this newly renovated 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom corner lot home. The open-concept layout includes a spacious living room, cozy family room, sunny breakfast area, and an elegant dining room. Modern upgrades encompass new flooring, garage door, stainless steel appliances, stylish cabinets, granite countertops and contemporary light fixtures. In 2022, the roof and HVAC including ductwork, were replaced ensuring worry free living. Step into the large fenced in backyard with separate patio and pool area. Don't miss out on this gem!
